    "These difficulties are due to several factors: the absence of leading figures, a preference for applied over fundamental research, the influence of science policy and inappropriate application of research findings [59].",
    "To overcome these challenges the proposed solutions, include securing independent research funding, enhancing scientometric databases, and fostering interdisciplinary research methods.",
